  "comment": "BTS200 LED Profiel Spot Zoom 200W Warm Wit: The BeamZ BTF300Z Fresnel Zoom uses a high power single source LED engine to provide a smooth and even field of warm white light, providing a modern replacement for traditional fresnels. The BTF300Z is equipped with high-quality optics, a motorized 8 - 47 degree zoom function and is both dimmable and able to be operated as a strobe up to 17 flashes per second. Ideal for use in theatres, studios, museums, exhibitions or any stage setting that requires smooth warm white output from an energy saving fixture with exceptionally long life. Features Powerconnector in&out and DMX controllability. Supplied with barndoors for beam shaping and glare reduction, safety cord and colour frame.\n\n",
